longBusinessSummary: Jintai Energy Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the energy trading business in the People's Republic of China. It trades in fuel oil and kerosene; operates digital trading parks; and provides customs declaration and oil drilling services. The company also provides oil and gas development engineering construction, and technical services, including geochemical exploration, drilled wells, test logging, downhole special operation, engineering building design, and construction services, as well as related oil and gas development technology research, development, and services; energy internet, which connects the energy industry chain with the Internet; and supply chain services that include integration of internet, massive of data, internet of things, storage, and finance, as well as operates industrial parks. In addition, it offers customs declaration services. The company was formerly known as Yuhua Energy Holdings Limited and changed its name to Jintai Energy Holdings Limited in February 2020. Jintai Energy Holdings Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Dongying, the People's Republic of China.
